name: collage: NOLA Summer
description: ‘21 was very much a transitional year. I moved out of NYC after 5 years with my eyes set on my hometown of Dallas, TX, but first I would stop for 3 months in the Big Easy. The culture was as thick as the air- inspiring music, murals, and food. There is no place like it of that I’m sure. New Orleans I can’t wait to see you again now that we are more familiar friends. | mp4 2048x2732 | damnsam
